## Setup Instructions

### 1. Prerequisites
- Ansible installed on control machine
- SSH access to target servers
- Sudo privileges on target servers
- Podman or Docker on target servers

### 2. Configure Inventory
Edit `inventory` file with your server IPs and credentials

### 3. Run Playbook
```bash
ansible-playbook -i inventory playbook.yml
```

### 4. Access Dashboards
- Grafana: http://metrics-hub-ip:3000 (admin/admin123)
- Prometheus: http://metrics-hub-ip:9090

